item.title: Sell Less, Connect More, and Raise Your Rates with Confidence with John Ray
item.description:
Most people undercharge not because they’re greedy, but because they underestimate their true value.

I had such an eye-opening conversation with John Ray—business advisor, pricing strategist, and author of The Generosity Mindset. We talked about why pricing is way more emotional than most people admit, and how confidence, perceived value, and intentional generosity all shape the way your business grows...
